<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0"/>
<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no">
<title>大奖抽不停</title>
<script>
    document.documentElement.style.fontSize = document.documentElement.clientWidth / 7.2 + 'px';
</script>
<link href="css/index.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap" v-show="!over">
	<div class="top">
		<img src="images/banner.jpg" alt="QQ阅读首次亮相快乐大本营" class="banner"/>
		<img :src=banner?"images/t1.png":"images/t2.png" alt="送阅券赢电影票" class="title auto-x"/>
		<div class="free auto-x">
			<img src="images/gift0.png" alt="书券">
			<span>领取200书券</span>
			<a href="javascript:;" class="getbtn" v-on:click="getTicket"></a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="cj">
		<div class="cjbtn auto-x">
			<img src="images/arrow.png" class="arrow auto-x" id="arrow">
			<img src="images/box.png" class="box" v-on:click="cjgame">
		</div>
		<img src="images/lights.png" class="lights auto-x" v-bind:class="{'shine':start}"/>
		<a href="javascript:;" alt="我的奖品" class="myprize auto-x" v-on:click="myprize"></a>
	</div>
	<div class="book">
		<div class="detail">
			<a href="javascript:ABook.gotoDetail(11366903);" class="bookc"></a>
			<p class="bname">爵迹</p>
			<p class="author">郭敬明</p>
			<a href="javascript:ABook.gotoDetail(11366903);" class="readbtn">立即阅读》</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="bottom">
		<a href="javascript:;" alt="如此好事，分享给好友" class="share" v-on:click="share"></a>
		<div class="rule">
			<strong>活动规则</strong>
			<p>
				1. 活动时间：2016年10月1日0点—10月3日0点<br>
				2. 书券总计1000万份，有效期30天，先到先得，送完即止，领取后30分钟内到账<br>
				3. 活动期间，同一用户仅有一次抽奖机会，奖品包括《爵迹》电影票和明星签名照（同一设备，同一QQ号/微信号均视为同一用户）<br>
				4. 明星签名照领取方式：抽中后请按提示<a href="javascript:Local.go('contact.html');">填写有效联系方式</a>，奖品将在活动结束后10个工作日内统一发放
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="over" id="over" v-bind:class="{'overshow':over}">
    <img src="images/over.png" alt="本期活动已结束">
</div>
<div class="mask" id="mask" v-bind:class="{'show':mask}">
    <div class="tiparea" id="tiparea1" v-show="!link">
        <h3>{{mtitle}}</h3>
        <p>{{mtip}}</p>
        <a href="javascript:;" class="knowbtn" v-on:click="closemask">我知道了</a>
    </div>
    <div class="tiparea" id="tiparea2" v-show="link">
    	<div class="prizepic">
    		<img v-bind:src=psrc v-bind:class="{'movie':movie}">
    	</div>
        <h2>
        	恭喜你<br>获得<span class="pname">{{pname}}</span>
        </h2>
        <p>{{ptip}}</p>
        <div v-show="movie">
        	<p>账号：{{ticketId}}</p>
        	<p>密码：{{ticketPwd}}</p>
        </div>
        <a href="javascript:;" class="closebtn" v-on:click="closemask"></a>
        <a href="javascript:;" class="knowbtn" v-show="movie" v-on:click="closemask">我知道了</a>
        <a href="javascript:Local.go('contact.html');" class="linkbtn" id="linkbtn" v-show="!movie">填写联系方式</a>
    </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/zepto-1.1.3.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/vue.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/jsbridge.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/local.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/common.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/abook.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="index.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://pingjs.qq.com/ping.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	if(typeof(pgvMain) == 'function'){
		pgvMain();
	}
</script>
</body>
</html>
